    {
        "url": "/quotes/tess_gerritsen_608275",
        "quote": "I think what medical training does is it gives you the language, the tools to look up facts. I think medical training gives you a sense of how to approach a problem, how to look at symptoms and go down the list of what it might be.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tess Gerritsen",
            "url": "/quotes/tess_gerritsen_608275"
