    {
        "url": "/quotes/tess_gerritsen_608246",
        "quote": "I met my husband, Jacob, in medical school. We married and went to live in Hawaii where his family lived. It was very beautiful, but I wasn't used to being on an island and needed wide open spaces. Eventually we moved to Maine, New England.",
