    {
        "url": "/quotes/tess_gerritsen_608249",
        "quote": "I think of myself as a fairly logical, scientific and somewhat reserved person. Maura Isles, the Boston medical examiner who appears in five of my books, is me. Almost everything I use in describing her, from her taste in wine to her biographical data, is taken from my own family. Except I don't have a serial killer as a mother!",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tess Gerritsen",
            "url": "/quotes/tess_gerritsen_608249"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Medical",
                "url": "/topics/medical"
